Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've made a great number of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with your new bond, you've obtained the Hanged Man Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bonds will continue to strengthen through your encounters and conversations,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as you gain a deeper understanding of one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I get to see Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Okay, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule an interview with the magazine tomorrow at 11:30 PM at our office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been crazy since she got the lead role for that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A costume check for the movie at 2:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a recording for a radio talk show at 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,filming for a commercial at 8:00, and we finish at 4:00 A.M.
