Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Risette! Risette! Risette! {This line continues down through the next 2 lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha— Wait! Hey, Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
