Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.98,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine your fans must be worried because of your sudden hiatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suffering from any health problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, my health isn't an issue or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it related to your mental health?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you'll be taking your break in Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means Risette is here for real! {This line is showing at the same time next 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Excuse me, but why a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rise has no further comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe an idol's coming out here! {Same time as line above and below}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll be back after a quick commercial break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has everything I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Balance will revitalize your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milk? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, isn't that her? {Same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, you take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No way! Isn't that Risette?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}did{\i0} give it back to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that strap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't your grandmother run a traditional tofu shop in Inaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know when you'll return to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, think we'll run into Rise? {Pretty sure Nanako says 'Rise-chan'}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So are you looking to retire? {Same time as line under}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro, you saw her? You saw Rise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't know. {Same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How will you be spending your time? {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool! Was she as cute as she is on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,100)}I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Inaba have those unresolved serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, we're out of time, {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best thing about this town was how quiet it was, but it's gotten crazy this past year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but stay tuned for these commercials. {same time as line above}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I'm the only {\i1}true{\i0} you.{what does this even mean?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For licensing, go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your Future"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Amagi, you know Rise's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marukyu is probably the traditional tofu shop they were referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We carry their tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we went by the tofu shop, we could see Rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Now isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cases are really linked with the TV, she might be targeted next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like Rise's never been on TV before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Rise's only connection with the late Ms. Yamano
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was that they appeared on one or two shows together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the fuss about her break, she's the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To top it all off, she's moving here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point. If our assumptions are correct, she fits the criteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadduya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he goes after Rise,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the killer is targeting people from this town who show up on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll debunk the theory that he's targeting people related to Ms. Yamano's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Oh, now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still don't know the killer's motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's got a grudge against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I got a shitload of people who hate my guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi, what about you? You ever piss anyone off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Yukiko! Everyone's done something bad without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, in any case, I have no idea what everyone's done to cause such animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can ask him about his motives after we catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we should keep an eye on Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure? Doesn't she seem kinda different?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chest! Those hips! And her beautiful, thin legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you looking at me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what? I gotta disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chie, Jiraiya is Hanamura's Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chie's is Tomoe. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you guys taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is Chie's? A "Chie Pet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should we check out the tofu shop? {same time as line above}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko and I have to run by the Faculty Office, {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chie's is the Chie Pet Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go! {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chie's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, this is for our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about seeing Rise in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the excuses already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of weirdos hanging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back now after coming all this way to see Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ex-excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see the notice? We're out of tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It-It's really R-Risette!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound so lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're the guy from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You already know each other? No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to get some tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we're sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six fried tofu fritters, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice ad lib!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six fried tofu fritters it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got attitude problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm glad we came. We're cleared our mission for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A job? Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you noticed anything strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything strange? Like a stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard of the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that program last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you watch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since I'd heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl on TV wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn that swimsuit in a promotional video.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my chest isn't that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person on that show might get kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet it's hard to follow, but we aren't lying or pullin' your chain. {same time as line below}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey! You're upsetting the neighbours, so beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{12 minute mark}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tch!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi Kanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, um... Oh right, we're here to get some fried tofu fritters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Adachi from the Inaba PD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are policemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've already heard, but this area has been dangerous as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you suddenly decide to take a break here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mean to scare you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a chance I could get kidnapped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three guys just warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's in town anyway, she should've asked our chief to help for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{For a safe future!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Protecting today so we have a tomorrow.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Digital TV}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came to warn Kujikawa Rise based on my detective's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could some high school kids who don't even know the situation beat me to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Courage:}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Fearless}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Diligence:}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Staunch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Understanding:}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Generous}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Expression:}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Eloquent}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Knowledge:}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Informed}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Yo, why are we stalking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}We might find the guy who's after Rise if we trail her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Keep your eyes peeled for any suspicious characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}We're the ones who look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}What on Earth are you guys doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}You look really suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Are you the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,713)}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do deliver everywhere, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the extra large.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's roast pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got Tokyo-style noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my steak over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other noodles are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here! The set's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's a detective doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima ordered me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, I overheard you making an order while doing some legwork for Dojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about timing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why do we have to eat with a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we haven't eaten yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me eat my tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hit the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave Risette to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami, you watch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, dammit! I'm gonna pummel ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! It'll be on the police if the suspect gets hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just your typical Risette-loving civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hardly "typical" after murdering people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save it for the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{MOEL Gas}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo! I've always wanted to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your help in apprehending the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on! Keep up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's all over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case is solved? Booyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he really was a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I really get kidnapped by a wimp like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see if someone's coming from any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to dealing with stalkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better if you weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{pink text: Kujikawa Rise}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{spread: Rise's perfect body!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{next page: Waiting for that special glance back at you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl everyone makes such a fuss over isn't the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risette, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a fictional character sold to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one sees the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!{fold cranes, acquire bitches}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I can do it if I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Text 0057}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.61,CellphoneEffortLess,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}From: Hanamura Yosuke\N{\fs20}Subject: The killer? has been caught.\N{\fs28}The killer? has been caught.\NHurry back with Risette.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the coast's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. It's getting dark out, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never told me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kujikawa Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard on the news last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Midnight Channel last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I caught a glimpse of her in the store when I passed by this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the variety show only starts up once they've entered the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we discuss how the person inside the TV could be producing the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could be subconsciously showing us their inner thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then what's up with the fuzzy program that comes on before they go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be the killer's warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is he warning? And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible that we're seeing the killer's thoughts, so it {\i1}looks{\i0} like a warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're seeing who he's targeting next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's his fantasies of "I'm gonna attack you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that mean the weirdo from earlier wasn't our guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know for sure is that Kujikawa Rise is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kujikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm transferring into one of the freshman classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to file the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's for sophomores.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're my senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to show me the ropes, Narukami.{She says "Narukami-Senpai"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred here last April myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't here when I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a different route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Daidara}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't sneak through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatsuhime Shrine}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your manager, I simply can't accept your decision to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an idol anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some puppet who needs someone to micromanage her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the movie you were just given the lead role for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to force me to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanami has taken your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanami? Mashita Kanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to support Kanami to the best of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you aren't deceiving yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved just for the hell of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't careful, you could get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna play, do it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two fighting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-Q! {She says this like "Maru-Kyun!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of Risettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this feel so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses, my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.00,0:24:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye... forever.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.72,0:22:12.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2}No time to waste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.31,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}but make you pace
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.31,0:22:15.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}It's okay to remove, copy, and paste
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.18,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}I'm doing my way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}You do it your way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.81,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't just follow your left, find the right way
Dialogue: 2,0:22:18.81,0:22:19.60,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Stereotypes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.60,0:22:20.52,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Too many hypes,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.23,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}But I'm the epitome of new types
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.23,0:22:23.73,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Having the fear is power to my soul
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.73,0:22:24.82,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}'Cause I overcome them
Dialogue: 2,0:22:24.82,0:22:25.57,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That's how I roll
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.24,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Expose your thoughts
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.70,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Don't be afraid of making mistakes
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Rules prevailing in
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.70,0:22:38.46,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}That may be your greatest rival
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.42,0:22:42.84,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Believe in faith and your heart
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Your true soul stop being in the shades
Dialogue: 2,0:22:47.42,0:22:52.05,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Come on, out in the open sun
Dialogue: 2,0:22:52.60,0:22:57.73,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of the child of destiny
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.40,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Delightful days
Dialogue: 2,0:23:01.81,0:23:06.19,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}are with rich density of love
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.99,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Thorny path
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.95,0:23:13.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}There's no easy way for real bliss
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.95,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}So I keep on fighting for
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.95,0:23:21.21,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(50,50)}Beauty of destiny
